   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Rule-Based EntityRuler Project\\n\",\"**NLP Project 28 of 100** — Combine spaCy's built-in NER with custom EntityRuler patterns for domain-specific entity extraction.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import spacy, subprocess, sys\\ntry: nlp = spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nexcept:\\n    subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','spacy','download','en_core_web_sm'])\\n    nlp = spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Add custom patterns\\nruler = nlp.add_pipe('entity_ruler', before='ner')\\npatterns = [\\n    {'label':'PRODUCT','pattern':'iPhone'},{'label':'PRODUCT','pattern':'MacBook'},\\n    {'label':'PRODUCT','pattern':'Tesla Model 3'},{'label':'PRODUCT','pattern':'PlayStation 5'},\\n    {'label':'TECH','pattern':'Python'},{'label':'TECH','pattern':'Kubernetes'},\\n    {'label':'TECH','pattern':'TensorFlow'},{'label':'TECH','pattern':'React'},\\n    {'label':'DEPT','pattern':'Engineering'},{'label':'DEPT','pattern':'Marketing'},\\n    {'label':'DEPT','pattern':'Human Resources'},{'label':'DEPT','pattern':'Finance'},\\n]\\nruler.add_patterns(patterns)\\nprint(f'Added {len(patterns)} custom patterns.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"texts = [\\n    'Apple released the new iPhone in Cupertino. The Engineering team at Google uses Python and TensorFlow.',\\n    'Tesla Model 3 sales surged in California. The Marketing department prepared the launch campaign.',\\n    'Microsoft hired 500 engineers for the Kubernetes team in Seattle. Human Resources processed all onboarding.',\\n]\\n\\nfor text in texts:\\n    doc = nlp(text)\\n    print(f'Text: {text[:60]}...')\\n    for ent in doc.ents:\\n        print(f'  {ent.label_:10s} → {ent.text}')\\n    print()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **EntityRuler adds domain-specific entities** that general NER misses.\\n\",\"- **Placing the ruler before NER** gives custom patterns priority.\\n\",\"- **Combine rule-based + ML NER** for comprehensive entity extraction.\\n\",\"- **For production, maintain entity dictionaries** as separate config files.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
